01:13:31.080 --> 01:13:32.081
No!

01:13:32.160 --> 01:13:33.321
No, Linda! No!

01:13:33.400 --> 01:13:34.481
Howard!

01:13:34.680 --> 01:13:36.842
Howard, the baby!

01:13:37.320 --> 01:13:39.004
